鯺字的康熙字典解释

【亥集中】【魚字部】　鯺； 康熙笔画：20； 页码：页1473第35
【集韻】專於切，音諸。與蠩同。蜛蠩，蟲名。一曰蝦蟆。又【正字通】蜛鯺，一頭數尾，長二三尺，左右有腳，狀如蠶，可食。又䱦鯺。詳䱦字註。

Kangxi dictionary interpretation of words
[Hai Collection] [Fish Character Department] 　鯺; Kangxi Strokes: 20; Pages: Page 1473 and 35
【Jiyun】Specializes in cutting and sound. Same as the pan. The worm, the name of the insect. One said prawns. Also [Zhengzitong] The small 鯺, one head and several tails, two or three feet long, with feet on the left and right, shaped like silkworms, and edible. And you ye. Detailed note of the word.
